These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Game: monopoly, poker, go, canasta
Music-Genre: indie, folk, jazz, salsa
1. Game:monopoly is on the right of Music-Genre:jazz##1
2. Music-Genre:salsa is on the far left##1
3. Music-Genre:jazz is between Music-Genre:folk and Game:poker##2
4. Game:canasta is on the far left##1
5. Game:go is between Game:poker and Game:monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | canasta         | poker   | go | monopoly       |
| Music-Genre      | salsa | indie | jazz   | folk |

