3. City:prague is on the right of City:nizza##1
4. Music-Genre:metal is on the left of City:nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | disco | metal | jazz | r&b |
| City   | new-york    | hannover   | nizza | prague       |

